Rules.InvariantScript:
With({TemSubMenu:!IsEmpty(ThisItem.SubMenu) && !IsBlank(ThisItem.SubMenu)},
    If(TemSubMenu,
        Set(varExpandedMenu,true);
        Set(varTargetScreen, ThisItem.Tela); // <- Captura da tela
        If(varItemMenuClicked.NomeTela=ThisItem.NomeTela && varShowSubMenu,
            Set(varShowSubMenu,false)
            ,
            Set(varShowSubMenu,true)
        )
        ,
        Set(varShowSubMenu,false); //close sub menu
        Set(varFillSelectedMenu,ThisItem); //fill menu item selected
        Set(varTargetScreen, ThisItem.Tela), // <- Captura da tela
        Navigate(ThisItem.Tela) //go to page 
    )
    ;

    Set(varItemMenuClicked,ThisItem); //menu item clicked
    Set(varItemSubMenuClicked,Blank()); //clear sub menu item
    Set(varTargetScreen, ThisItem.Tela); // <- Captura da tela
    Navigate(ThisItem.Tela);

    app_cpn_vincy_notificacoes.OnSelect() //run any action
)
